{
    "slot": "veemod goggles", 
    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block\">A veemod (\"vision enhancement module\") is a narrow crystalline strip that slots into a set of veemod goggles to enhance the goggles' use. Inserting a veemod into a pair of goggles is a standard action that provokes attacks of opportunity. Veemods are color-coded items, and provide the following benefits.</p>", 
    "name": "Veemod", 
    "weight": "-", 
    "url": "pfsrd://Technology Guide/Rules/Equipment/Gear/Technological Gear/On Signals/Veemod", 
    "type": "item", 
